            <p>&#34;Jerusalem &#40;Holy City&#41; the Glory of all Lands.&#34;¬ù<lb/>
                ALFRED A. MARCUS&#44;<lb/>
                Diamond Merchant and Importer&#44;<lb/>
                PURCHASER OF REAL ESTATE &#40;LANDED PROPERTY&#41;.<lb/>
                Residence&#44; 127 DARTMOUTH STREET.<lb/></p>
            <p>No business will be transacted or interviews had on the Jewish Sabbath&#44; from one hour before sunset<lb/> on Friday until one hour after sunset on Saturday&#44; or on the Jewish Festivals&#44; and no letters will be<lb/> opened on those days.<lb/></p>
            <p>Boston Feby 2. A. M. 5642<lb/></p>
            <p>Revd. S. Morais<lb/>
                My very dear Sir &#38; friend<lb/></p>
            <p>Your&#39;s received &#38; receive<lb/> my very sincere thanks for your very<lb/> kind advice it is quite true what you<lb/> say.  I often wish I had you near me<lb/> to consult &#38; advise do not think I<lb/> am a very rich man I have very large<lb/> &#38; extensive interest in Real Estate &#38;<lb/> Water Power Bonds&#44; &#38;  my business is<lb/> one of large anxieties but whenever I<lb/> make a profit.  I try as far as his<lb/> in my power to devote at the least<lb/> one seventh to charitable purposes.<lb/>  My &#91;crossed&#45;out&#93; aim in life as well as my<lb/> beloved family is to try &#38; support<lb/> orthodox Judaism to shew those<lb/> miserable Reformers the purity of<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>faith please tell the owner of<lb/> the &#91;Hebrew&#93; to select&#91;&#63;&#93; it here next<lb/> Tuesday on approval &#38; if it suits<lb/> I will R&#91;&#63;&#93;ss it or <del>rent</del> return at once.<lb/>  Regarding our distressed brethren in<lb/> Russia I hope in my next to<lb/> let you know what I hope with<lb/> God Blessings to do for them.<lb/>  What is your congregation doing<lb/> My idea of the <sic>Souveneir</sic> Card<lb/> was to hand the copyright over to<lb/> the Garfield Hospital at Washington<lb/> I thought if they undertook its sale<lb/> &#38; the Perkins Institute for Blind<lb/> it would realise largely.<lb/></p>
            <p>With the most sincere respect<lb/> &#38; esteem in which my beloved<lb/> wife daughter &#38; son unite &#38; regards<lb/> to all dear I remain<lb/></p>
            <p>to you		Yours faithfully<lb/>
                Alfred A Marcus<lb/></p>
        </body>
